desc: Wild Atlantic Hemp is a family run farm in County Clare, Ireland. We grow cannabis in Living Soil and produce a CBD oil using a solvent free process. We are approved for the processing of cannabis as a food by the Health Service Executive and a registered Health Food Supplement with the Food Safety Authority of Ireland

layout.text: Wild Atlantic Hemp is a family-run farm in County Clare growing Cannabis in Living Soil and producing CBD oil through a solvent-free process.
